review_data: Reviewed in the United States on October 10, 2018
name: Amazon Customer
title: Outdated
review: I purchased this product the end of July 2018, when I took the box out to make a batch of yogurt I noticed that the expiration date on the package was March 2018. I also had to pay a relative high amount of shipping as it came from Bulgaria, Too bad since I was looking forward to trying the taste.
